# nonebot-plugin-antiinsult
  
**NoneBot 反嘴臭插件**  
  

<a href="./LICENSE">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/license/tkgs0/nonebot-plugin-antiinsult.svg" alt="license">
</a>
<a href="https://pypi.python.org/pypi/nonebot-plugin-antiinsult">
